sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Administrator
    participant S as System
    A->>S: Select Bin for Deactivation
    S->>A: Prompt for Reason (Damaged, Replaced, Inactive)
    A->>S: Provide Reason & Confirm
    S->>S: Update Bin Status to 'Deactivated'
    S->>S: Remove from Active Routes
    S->>A: Confirm Deactivation